{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Receipts provide a valuable record of the sale for an app or for any In-App Purchases made from within an app. You can add receipt validation code to your app to prevent unauthorized purchases and protect your content. Learn how to verify exactly what people have paid for and how to validate these transactions."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Overview","type":"heading","anchor":"overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","type":"reference"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"WWDC14","role":"sampleCode","title":"Preventing Unauthorized Purchases with Receipts","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}]},"kind":"article","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc14-305-preventing-unauthorized-purchases-with-receipts"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex","identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2014\/305\/","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC14-305-Preventing-Unauthorized-Purchases-with-Receipts"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC14"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC14":{"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc14","abstract":[{"text":"Xcode 6, Swift 1.0, iOS 8, macOS 10.10 (Yosemite).","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentat